com.krobothsoftware.commons.parse

Interface ParserInitializable

  • All Known Implementing Classes:
    Parser, ParserHtmlCleaner, ParserJson

    public interface ParserInitializable
    Parser can init parsers before they are needed. Usually, a Parser initiates parsing components when needed depending on Handler type.
    Since:
    SNC 1.0

    • Method Summary

      Methods 
      Modifier and Type Method and Description
      void init()
      Initializes parser components and Ignores any throwables.

    • Method Detail

      • init

        void init()
        Initializes parser components and Ignores any throwables. May log report. If there is an error, it will arise when parser tries to create it again when needed.

        Do not call this method if you don't need access to parsers, or pre-initiation.

        Since:
        SNC 1.0
